Thank you for coming.

26
00:02:01,340 --> 00:02:02,180
Here.

27
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:07,300
You're the new singer, huh?

28
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:08,260
Yes, she's my sister.

29
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:10,260
They're sisters.

30
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:12,300
Real sisters?

31
00:02:12,300 --> 00:02:13,140
Exactly.

32
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,340
The two of you

33
